author: veithen
msg: Moved the admin console related code from axis2-transport-http to axis2-webapp. Reason:
* It doesn't make sense to split the view part (JSP pages; axis2-webapp) and the controller part (AdminAgent and AxisAdminServlet; axis2-transport-http) over two different projects!
* The admin console is tightly coupled to Axis2, so everything should be moved there.
